With this migration, **all reasoning and tool routing live in a clean Python micro‑service,** giving you built‑in retries, guardrails, and trace inspection, while your Next .js UI stays lean and responsive. Students issue natural‑language commands; the agent returns a bounded set of actions; the 3‑D canvas and physics engine update instantly.

**Ignition sequence complete—lift‑off!** 🚀
